title: KINO (Victor Tsoi) - Voysko Let (Time Warriors)
description:
This is a fanmade compilation (created by one fan and remastered by other) of a non-album tracks by russian rock-group 'KINO'. Most interesting fragment of this disc is a new song 'Ataman' from last year, that was recorded by survived members of the band over a rough demo that was made by the frontman of the band, Victor Tsoi, in 1990, just a few months before his death in a car accident. This compilation is published in lossless for a first time.
